head: District Court.
p: The District Court of Olympia was convened at 10 o'clock this morning, Hon. O. Jacobs, C. J., presiding. Below we present a list of the cases on the docket:
Oregon Steam Navigation Company vs. Hale, Crosby et al.
Board of Regents of Washington Territory University vs. Allen C. Smith et ux.
J. D. Mabie vs. L. A. Davis and L. J. Davis.
T. F> McElroy vs. A.J. Miller & Co.
W. J. Waitt vs. Oregon Steam Navigation Company.
Barlow & Sheppard vs. George Cogan, surviving partner of Molony & Coggan.
